<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NEXUS — Sustainable Autonomous Navigation System</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;700;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --void:#050a0e;--bg:#030b12;--bg2:#060f1a;--bg3:#0a1622;
  --G:#3bff14;--B:#00f0ff;--A:#ffcd00;--V:#9b7fff;
  --text:#cceee8;--text-dim:rgba(204,238,232,.55);--text-muted:rgba(204,238,232,.28);
  --border:rgba(0,240,255,.12);--border-b:rgba(0,240,255,.35);
  --mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;--disp:'Orbitron',monospace;--ser:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--void);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;overflow-x:hidden;}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;
  background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(0,240,255,.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,240,255,.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(rgba(0,240,255,.07) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,240,255,.07) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:20px 20px,20px 20px,100px 100px,100px 100px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;}
body::after{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 3px,rgba(0,0,0,.04) 3px,rgba(0,0,0,.04) 4px);pointer-events:none;z-index:999;}

/* NAV */
.topbar{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:52px;background:rgba(5,10,14,.93);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 48px;z-index:500;gap:20px;}
.topbar::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--B),transparent);}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--disp);font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--B);}
.logo-d{width:12px;height:12px;background:var(--B);transform:rotate(45deg);flex-shrink:0;}
.back-a{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color .2s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.back-a::before{content:'◀';font-size:8px;}
.back-a:hover{color:var(--B);}
.vol{margin-left:auto;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--text-muted);}
.sdot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--G);display:inline-block;margin-right:6px;animation:blink 2s infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:.2;}}

/* HERO */
#hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center;padding:100px 48px 80px;position:relative;z-index:1;overflow:hidden;}
.hcorn{position:absolute;width:24px;height:24px;}
.hcorn::before,.hcorn::after{content:'';position:absolute;background:rgba(0,240,255,.35);}
.hcorn.tl{top:68px;left:48px;}.hcorn.tl::before{top:0;left:0;width:1px;height:24px;}.hcorn.tl::after{top:0;left:0;width:24px;height:1px;}
.hcorn.tr{top:68px;right:48px;}.hcorn.tr::before{top:0;right:0;width:1px;height:24px;}.hcorn.tr::after{top:0;right:0;width:24px;height:1px;}
.hcorn.bl{bottom:40px;left:48px;}.hcorn.bl::before{bottom:0;left:0;width:1px;height:24px;}.hcorn.bl::after{bottom:0;left:0;width:24px;height:1px;}
.hcorn.br{bottom:40px;right:48px;}.hcorn.br::before{bottom:0;right:0;width:1px;height:24px;}.hcorn.br::after{bottom:0;right:0;width:24px;height:1px;}
.hcoord{position:absolute;font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:.06em;}
.hcoord.tl{top:72px;left:80px;}.hcoord.tr{top:72px;right:80px;}.hcoord.bl{bottom:44px;left:80px;}.hcoord.br{bottom:44px;right:80px;}
.hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;}
.ntitle-wrap{position:relative;margin-bottom:20px;}
.ntitle{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:clamp(80px,14vw,180px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.18em;
  color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1.5px var(--B);
  filter:drop-shadow(0 0 28px rgba(0,240,255,.3)) drop-shadow(0 0 70px rgba(0,240,255,.1));
  animation:fadeUp .8s .1s ease both;}
.ntitle-fill{position:absolute;inset:0;font-family:var(--disp);font-size:clamp(80px,14vw,180px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.18em;
  color:var(--B);opacity:.07;clip-path:inset(0 100% 0 0);animation:scan 2s .6s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards;}
@keyframes scan{to{clip-path:inset(0 0% 0 0);}}
.sysname{font-size:clamp(10px,1.2vw,14px);letter-spacing:.35em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:18px;animation:fadeUp .8s .25s ease both;}
.tagline{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0;border:1px solid var(--border-b);padding:9px 22px;border-radius:100px;
  font-size:clamp(10px,1.1vw,12px);letter-spacing:.08em;color:rgba(0,240,255,.45);margin-bottom:52px;animation:fadeUp .8s .4s ease both;}
.tagline span{opacity:.4;margin:0 10px;}
.meta-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);width:100%;max-width:900px;animation:fadeUp .8s .55s ease both;}
.mcell{background:var(--bg2);padding:18px 22px;text-align:left;}
.mc-lbl{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(0,240,255,.4);margin-bottom:7px;}
.mc-val{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.6;}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

/* SECTIONS */
section{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:100px 80px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
.eyebrow{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.28em;color:rgba(0,240,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.eyebrow::before{content:'//';color:var(--text-muted);}
.eyebrow::after{content:'';height:1px;width:40px;background:var(--border-b);}
.secnum{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:12px;}
.sectitle{font-family:var(--ser);font-size:clamp(34px,4.5vw,58px);font-weight:300;color:var(--text);line-height:1.0;margin-bottom:52px;}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(26px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease;}
.reveal.vis{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

/* CANVAS CONTAINERS — key fix: explicit height on wrapper */
.cvs-wrap{
  border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  width:100%;
}
.cvs-wrap canvas{
  display:block;
  width:100% !important;
  height:100% !important;
  position:absolute;top:0;left:0;
}
.figcap{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:12px;text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.figcap::before{content:'FIG';color:rgba(0,240,255,.35);}

/* CHALLENGE */
.ch3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:40px;}
.chcard{background:var(--bg);padding:30px 26px;transition:background .2s;}
.chcard:hover{background:var(--bg2);}
.chn{font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:.2em;margin-bottom:14px;}
.cht{font-family:var(--ser);font-size:19px;font-weight:300;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.2;}
.chb{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;}
.chstat{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:26px;font-weight:700;}
.chsl{font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-top:4px;}

/* DESIGN SYSTEM */
.ds2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:56px;align-items:start;margin-bottom:40px;}
.swrow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:12px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);margin-bottom:10px;transition:border-color .2s;}
.swrow:hover{border-color:var(--border-b);}
.swdot{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;}
.swname{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px;}
.swhex{font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:2px;}
.swmean{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-dim);}
.swsem{font-size:9px;color:rgba(0,240,255,.4);margin-top:2px;}
.dstext p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:16px;}
.dstext strong{color:var(--text);}
.dstext em{font-family:var(--ser);font-style:italic;color:rgba(0,240,255,.4);}
.dsfeat{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-top:18px;}
.dsf{padding:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-dim);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:7px;}
.dsf::before{content:'◆';color:var(--B);font-size:8px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}

/* INTERFACE */
.hdiv{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin:56px 0;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.3em;color:var(--text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;}
.hdiv::before,.hdiv::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--border),transparent);}
.hdiv::after{background:linear-gradient(270deg,var(--border),transparent);}
.f2col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:72px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:72px;}
.f2col.rev{direction:rtl;}.f2col.rev>*{direction:ltr;}
.feyebrow{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(0,240,255,.4);margin-bottom:10px;}
.ftitle{font-family:var(--ser);font-size:28px;font-weight:300;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.2;}
.fbody{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:18px;}
.fbody strong{color:var(--text);}
.specg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;}
.spec{padding:11px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);}
.speclbl{font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:4px;}
.specval{font-size:10px;color:rgba(0,240,255,.5);}

/* SCREENS */
.scwrap{border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:28px;}
.scwrap img{width:100%;display:block;filter:brightness(.95) contrast(1.04);transition:filter .4s;}
.scwrap:hover img{filter:brightness(1.0) contrast(1.07);}

/* IMPACT */
.imp3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:22px;margin-bottom:44px;}
.icard{padding:34px 26px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.icard::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .9s ease;}
.icard.i1::after{background:var(--B);}.icard.i2::after{background:var(--G);}.icard.i3::after{background:var(--A);}
.icard.vis::after{transform:scaleX(1);}
.inum{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:48px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:7px;}
.iunit{font-size:18px;opacity:.6;}
.ilbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:5px;font-weight:500;}
.isub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;}
.ivs{font-size:9px;margin-top:8px;letter-spacing:.1em;}

/* STRAT LABEL */
.slabel{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(0,240,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;}

/* CONCLUSION */
.concl{max-width:820px;padding:46px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);position:relative;margin-bottom:72px;}
.concl::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--B),transparent);}
.concl::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--B));}
.concl p{font-family:var(--ser);font-size:clamp(17px,2vw,24px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text);font-style:italic;}

footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:38px 80px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.fl{font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:.12em;line-height:1.8;}
.fr{display:flex;gap:22px;}
.fa{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s;}
.fa:hover{color:var(--B);}

@media(max-width:900px){
  section{padding:60px 24px;}#hero{padding:90px 24px 60px;}
  .meta-grid,.ch3,.imp3{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .ds2,.f2col{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.f2col.rev{direction:ltr;}
  footer{flex-direction:column;gap:16px;padding:24px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="topbar">
  <a href="./index.html" class="back-a">Portfolio</a>
  <div class="logo"><div class="logo-d"></div>NX-SYS</div>
  <div class="vol"><span class="sdot"></span>VOL. 01 / 2025 — ACTIVE</div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hcorn tl"></div><div class="hcorn tr"></div><div class="hcorn bl"></div><div class="hcorn br"></div>
  <div class="hcoord tl">NX-SYS · V2.1.0</div><div class="hcoord tr">VOL. 01 / 2025</div>
  <div class="hcoord bl">GSAPP × ADD+ON</div><div class="hcoord br">Q3 2023 SPRINT</div>
  <!-- hero bg canvas -->
  <canvas id="cvs-hero" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;display:block;"></canvas>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="ntitle-wrap">
      <div class="ntitle">NEXUS</div>
      <div class="ntitle-fill">NEXUS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sysname">Sustainable Autonomous Navigation System</div>
    <div class="tagline">Beyond Coordinates<span>·</span>Intuitive Intelligence<span>·</span>Conscious Journey</div>
    <div class="meta-grid">
      <div class="mcell"><div class="mc-lbl">Role</div><div class="mc-val">System Designer<br>Product Designer</div></div>
      <div class="mcell"><div class="mc-lbl">Duration</div><div class="mc-val">4-Week Design Sprint<br>Q3 2023</div></div>
      <div class="mcell"><div class="mc-lbl">Skills</div><div class="mc-val">Cross-Device Experience<br>UX Design · Design Systems</div></div>
      <div class="mcell"><div class="mc-lbl">Tools</div><div class="mc-val">Figma · Blender<br>After Effects · Principle</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 1.0 CHALLENGE -->
<section id="challenge">
  <div class="eyebrow">The Problem</div>
  <div class="secnum">1.0</div>
  <h2 class="sectitle">The Challenge:<br>Attention Crisis</h2>
  <div class="ch3 reveal">
    <div class="chcard">
      <div class="chn">CHALLENGE 01</div>
      <div class="cht">The "Screenification" Problem</div>
      <p class="chb">Modern vehicles force constant focus-switching between road (far-field) and screen (near-field), causing cognitive overload and increased reaction time.</p>
      <div class="chstat" style="color:#ff4466">40<span style="font-size:16px">%</span></div>
      <div class="chsl">↑ Increase in reaction time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="chcard">
      <div class="chn">CHALLENGE 02</div>
      <div class="cht">The "Disconnected" Driver</div>
      <p class="chb">Standard GPS treats the car as a solitary object in static space — ignoring rich V2X Smart City data, resulting in stop-and-go driving patterns.</p>
      <div class="chstat" style="color:var(--A)">0</div>
      <div class="chsl">V2X contextual awareness</div>
    </div>
    <div class="chcard">
      <div class="chn">THE CORE QUESTION</div>
      <div class="cht">Chaotic Task → Seamless Flow</div>
      <p class="chb">How do we design a cockpit that informs without distracting — transforming the daily commute from a chaotic task into a seamless flow state?</p>
      <div class="chstat" style="color:var(--G)">→</div>
      <div class="chsl">From demand to ambient</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cvs-wrap reveal" style="height:380px;"><canvas id="cvs-challenge"></canvas></div>
  <div class="figcap reveal">1.1 — Attention fragmentation · Road (far-field) vs Screen (near-field) · V2X gap · Chaotic→Seamless design question</div>
</section>

<!-- 2.0 STRATEGY -->
<section id="strategy">
  <div class="eyebrow">Design Strategy</div>
  <div class="secnum">2.0</div>
  <h2 class="sectitle">Three Pillars of<br>Sustainable Autonomy</h2>
  <div class="slabel reveal">2.1 — Paradigm Transformation</div>
  <div class="cvs-wrap reveal" style="height:280px;margin-bottom:28px;"><canvas id="cvs-paradigm"></canvas></div>
  <div class="figcap reveal">2.1 — More Screens (distraction) → Better Communication (V2X + Ambient) → Conscious Journey (Mind + Body)</div>
  <div class="slabel reveal" style="margin-top:48px;">2.2 — Beyond Coordinates: V2X Contextual Awareness</div>
  <div class="cvs-wrap reveal" style="height:300px;margin-bottom:28px;"><canvas id="cvs-v2x"></canvas></div>
  <div class="figcap reveal">2.2 — Coordinates Only (reactive) → Vehicle-Infrastructure (V2X data) → Proactive Reaction (unseen hazards)</div>
  <div class="slabel reveal" style="margin-top:48px;">2.3 — System Decision Logic</div>
  <div class="cvs-wrap reveal" style="height:400px;margin-bottom:28px;"><canvas id="cvs-flow"></canvas></div>
  <div class="figcap reveal">2.3 — Vehicle enters smart zone → V2X signal → confidence threshold → Green Wave / Ghost Object / Ambient Alert / Eco Arrival</div>
</section>

<!-- 3.0 DESIGN SYSTEM -->
<section id="design-system">
  <div class="eyebrow">Visual Language</div>
  <div class="secnum">3.0</div>
  <h2 class="sectitle">Design System:<br>Bioluminescent Aesthetic</h2>
  <div class="ds2">
    <div>
      <div class="slabel reveal" style="margin-bottom:16px;">Electroluminescent Bioluminescence — Color Semantics</div>
      <div class="swrow reveal"><div class="swdot" style="background:#050a0e;border:1px solid rgba(0,240,255,.25)"></div><div><div class="swname">VOID BLACK</div><div class="swhex">#050A0E</div><div class="swmean">Background · OLED efficiency</div><div class="swsem">Night Vision Preserved</div></div></div>
      <div class="swrow reveal" style="transition-delay:.06s"><div class="swdot" style="background:#3bff14;box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(59,255,20,.4)"></div><div><div class="swname">BIO-GREEN</div><div class="swhex">#3BFF14</div><div class="swmean">Flow state · Optimal speed · Regenerative braking</div><div class="swsem">Responsive Driving</div></div></div>
      <div class="swrow reveal" style="transition-delay:.12s"><div class="swdot" style="background:#00f0ff;box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,240,255,.4)"></div><div><div class="swname">ELECTRIC BLUE</div><div class="swhex">#00F0FF</div><div class="swmean">V2X connected · Smart city grid · Infrastructure</div><div class="swsem">Infrastructure Link</div></div></div>
      <div class="swrow reveal" style="transition-delay:.18s"><div class="swdot" style="background:#ffcd00;box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(255,205,0,.35)"></div><div><div class="swname">AMBER</div><div class="swhex">#FFCD00</div><div class="swmean">Prediction · Traffic forecast · Proactive alerts</div><div class="swsem">So in Red Light</div></div></div>
      <div class="swrow reveal" style="transition-delay:.24s"><div class="swdot" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3bff14,#00f0ff);box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(59,255,20,.2)"></div><div><div class="swname">LIVING LIGHT</div><div class="swhex">Dynamic</div><div class="swmean">Data breathes · Biological signal · Organism mimicry</div><div class="swsem">Organism Velocity</div></div></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="dstext reveal" style="transition-delay:.1s">
        <p>Inspired by <em>deep-sea organisms</em>, the visual language is <strong>functional, not merely aesthetic</strong> — designed for low-light driving environments where visual fatigue is a safety concern.</p>
        <p>Each color carries <strong>semantic meaning</strong>, creating an intuitive hierarchy that drivers decode at a glance — bypassing cognitive overhead that text-icon interfaces demand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cvs-wrap reveal" style="height:260px;margin-top:18px;" id="biolum-wrap"><canvas id="cvs-biolum"></canvas></div>
      <div class="dsfeat reveal" style="transition-delay:.15s">
        <div class="dsf">High contrast on dark backgrounds for clarity</div>
        <div class="dsf">Semantic color coding for intuitive understanding</div>
        <div class="dsf">Glowing effects that mimic natural bioluminescence</div>
        <div class="dsf">Accessibility-compliant color combinations</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 4.0 INTERFACE -->
<section id="interface">
  <div class="eyebrow">Interface Features</div>
  <div class="secnum">4.0</div>
  <h2 class="sectitle">The "Glass Box" Experience</h2>

  <div class="hdiv">4.1 / AR-HUD: Green Wave Tunnel · Ghost Objects · Direct Overlay</div>
  <div class="f2col reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="feyebrow">Feature 4.1 — AR-HUD</div>
      <h3 class="ftitle">Visualizing the Unseen</h3>
      <p class="fbody"><strong>Green Wave Tunnel</strong> — Floating semi-transparent green hoops projected onto the lane. GLOSA calculates perfect velocity to hit every green light.</p>
      <p class="fbody">When V2X detects a cyclist behind a building, the HUD renders a <strong>Ghost outline</strong> — giving the driver X-Ray vision before the hazard is physically visible.</p>
